					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I know that on the SNES, DRAM refresh halts the CPU for 40 master cycles every line.  Do the Genesis and NES CPUs have to be halted during DRAM refresh, or do they use some other kind of DRAM that doesn't need halting the CPU.</div>

