					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">NES CPU doesn't use DRAM.<br /><br />The sprite memory in the PPU is DRAM, but its refresh is the same as evaluation.<br /><br />The FDS uses DRAM, but it seems to be using some kind of hidden refresh.</div>

